title: Central Perks Coffee House
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Organic, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A full service espresso bar with a relaxing atmosphere and secure Wi-Fi, located inside the historic Weisman Center. Offers an extensive vegan menu of sandwiches, salads, and burgers--made with organic and local ingredients whenever possible. Sample items include the vegan reuben sandwich, raspberry chipotle burger, and Central Perks gourmet un-tuna salad.
